  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK485">
<l>kālam karuti yiruppar kalaṅkātu</l>
<l> ñālaṅ karutu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They who thoughtfully consider and wait for the (right) time (for action), may successfully meditate (the conquest of) the world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
